file.name: LambdaCalc-test-oas30.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.1"
info:
  title: "LambdaCalc"
  version: "2019-04-29T03:42:17Z"
servers:
- url: "https://t8nhzdycmd.execute-api.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/{basePath}"
  variables:
    basePath:
      default: "/test"
paths:
  /calc:
    get:
      parameters:
      - name: "operand2"
        in: "query"
        required: true
        schema:
          type: "string"
      - name: "operator"
        in: "query"
        required: true
        schema:
          type: "string"
      - name: "operand1"
        in: "query"
        required: true
        schema:
          type: "string"
      responses:
        200:
          description: "200 response"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Empty"
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Input"
        required: true
      responses:
        200:
          description: "200 response"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Empty"
  /calc/{operand1}/{operand2}/{operator}:
    get:
      parameters:
      - name: "operand2"
        in: "path"
        required: true
        schema:
          type: "string"
      - name: "operator"
        in: "path"
        required: true
        schema:
          type: "string"
      - name: "operand1"
        in: "path"
        required: true
        schema:
          type: "string"
      responses:
        200:
          description: "200 response"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Result"
components:
  schemas:
    Empty:
      title: "Empty Schema"
      type: "object"
    Input:
      title: "Input"
      type: "object"
      properties:
        a:
          type: "number"
        b:
          type: "number"
        op:
          type: "string"
    Output:
      title: "Output"
      type: "object"
      properties:
        c:
          type: "number"
    Result:
      title: "Output"
      type: "object"
      properties:
        input:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/Input"
        output:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/Output"
